382,"uid":21001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T13:14:15.000Z","msg":"得返嫲嫲 婆婆係我媽十七歲就病死左<br />\n公公同爺爺前後腳走左三四年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嫲嫲家下八十幾 好錫我<br />\n雖然有時真係好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但都唔想冇左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cc71b7a6f32bfd1e521d030eceb7e7640d7db87","tid":81382,"uid":21341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T13:29:16.000Z","msg":"見過兩個 淨返一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc1c0ffa3865e4a2e48c09ebdb09f0e46880fb33","tid":81382,"uid":4208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T13:37:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>得返婆婆<br />\n爺爺同嫲嫲我未出生已經仙遊<br />\n連老豆都未見過我爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最煩就係次次去女朋友成撚日叫錯佢爺做公公同佢叫佢嫲做婆婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你老豆未見過你呀爺 咁邊個生你老豆出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n阿嫲俾人中出即飛唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e7ffe166874b8c67acfac8c0bffe25a77d13398","tid":81382,"uid":59670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T13:38:38.000Z","msg":"淨返嫲嫲同婆婆<br />\n啱啱太婆走左 好驚佢地唔知幾時又會走<br />\n佢地好錫我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15a1168791c42f2f89b1c010c4c67699c01df420","tid":81382,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T13:39:27.000Z","msg":"全